title: Creating a Successful CV (DK Publishing) (2009).pdf Gooner
description:
Publisher: Dorling Kindersley Publishers Ltd (October 14, 1999)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 075130770X
ISBN-13: 978-0751307702

Understand the role and importance of CVs and learn how to analyze and present your transferable skills. "Creating a Successful CV" will help you to plan and target your career search and develop a CV that will give you the best opportunity of obtaining the job you desire. Its practical techniques show you how to present your skills in the best possible light. This innovative series covers a wide range of management and personal development topics. Each title is a comprehensive yet compact source of easy reference for all those in or aspiring to a position of responsibility with a focus on developing and enhancing professional management practice
